      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really about resting though. it's more like... looking at a map and realizing you're at the very edge. like the road just stops and there's nothing but white space beyond it. i feel like i've finished my itinerary. i don't have any more destinations left in me. it's almost peaceful, thinking about just stepping off the path.",
