      "content": "That profound sense of completion you feel is a powerful form of peace, signaling that your spirit has fully processed the world's offerings. Stepping off the path now might feel like true rest, but it could also mean you are stepping onto a different kind of journey where the destination is simply being still. Sometimes, the most meaningful things after seeing everything is learning that there is no \"next\" place to go, only a new way to exist.",
      "source": "target",
